comment:
* This class represents the description of an inline suggestion. It contains information to help
 * the IME to decide where and when to show the suggestions. See {@link InlineSuggestion} for more
 * information.

variables.name: SOURCE_AUTOFILL
variables.comment: * Suggestion source: the suggestion is made by the user selected autofill service.

variables.name: SOURCE_PLATFORM
variables.comment: * Suggestion source: the suggestion is made by the platform.

variables.name: TYPE_SUGGESTION
variables.comment: * UI type: the UI contains an Autofill suggestion that will autofill the fields when tapped.

variables.name: TYPE_ACTION
variables.comment: * UI type: the UI contains an widget that will launch an intent when tapped.

variables.name: mInlinePresentationSpec
variables.comment: The presentation spec to which the inflated suggestion view abides.

variables.name: mSource
variables.comment: The source from which the suggestion is provided.

variables.name: mAutofillHints
variables.comment: Hints for the type of data being suggested.

variables.name: mPinned
variables.comment: Whether the suggestion should be pinned or not.

methods.name: public static InlineSuggestionInfo newInlineSuggestionInfo(@NonNull InlinePresentationSpec presentationSpec, @NonNull @Source String source, @SuppressLint("NullableCollection") @Nullable String[] autofillHints, @NonNull @Type String type, boolean isPinned)
